{"tid":1960244,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"扯！女列車長勸男乘客戴口罩　反遭「戳胸」","createTime":"2020-04-06T04:40:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-08T06:50:38.000Z","uid":209657,"like":149,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":57,"replies":[{"pid":"93953ffcb5be996c42fe95fd656f508fb1b4f7fa","tid":1960244,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T04:40:38.000Z","msg":"台灣交通部宣布四月份開始，搭乘大眾運輸交通工具，必須配戴口罩，否則拒載。台鐵實施後發生首例脫序案件，一名60出頭歲的何姓男子在瑞芳站上車後，口罩脫脫戴戴，楊姓女列車長為了避免恐慌，上前勸阻時，該名何姓男子竟對女列車長飆罵3字經還用手戳女列車長胸部。女列車長眼見無法單獨處理該名誇張乘客，拒絕開車，通報鐵路警察協助。<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/04/06/2490381-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F04%2F06%2F2490381-XXL.jpg&h=8870cb03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n根據了解，何姓男乘客在瑞芳站上車後，無故口罩反覆脫下戴上，到了百福站時，又脱下口罩，列車長上前勸阻時，何姓男乘客不但不願意配合，甚至飆罵三字經，<span style=\"color: red;\">還用手戳女列車長的胸口</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，列車長眼見情況即將失控，直接報警；七堵所警員趕抵現場時，勸告何姓男乘客戴好口罩，不能無故脫口罩，男子配合戴回口罩，但列車長為了避免造成擴大恐慌，便表示與該男解除運送契約，站方與台鐵人員便帶其離開車站，並轉搭乘計程車離去。"},{"pid":"772f38766d0f56bd296494dc9504d0a4b0e78197","tid":1960244,"uid":3241,"like":66,"dislike":8,"score":58,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T04:41:47.000Z","msg":"究竟係直取乳溝位置定係左右路突入呢"},{"pid":"c4b0f1ac186eaa09810ab909e4719a4101980e79","tid":1960244,"uid":2507,"like":112,"dislike":2,"score":110,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T04:42:05.000Z","msg":"好耐冇睇過呢類台灣新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eff10a3a3a6457bdc08ec8945a8f9a2ebde5f3c1","tid":1960244,"uid":35699,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T04:42:44.000Z","msg":"百福 +1？？？"},{"pid":"ca637698cb6cb8941265ce2a8b81690db36038e4","tid":1960244,"uid":209657,"like":23,"dislike":2,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T04:42:50.000Z","msg":"發生意外插曲的台鐵4121次區間車，因此晚點25分鐘，但當下，其他台鐵人員立即應變處理，協助原列車上的的乘客，搭乘下一班列車。事後，該名女列車長心情大受影響，但台鐵力挺車長作為，肯定女列車長當下處置得宜，以維護車長與車上旅客之安危。也對脫序的何姓男乘客保留法律追訴權。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/04/06/2490382-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F04%2F06%2F2490382-XXL.jpg&h=ffee19f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/04/06/2490383-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F04%2F06%2F2490383-XXL.jpg&h=644b559c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"deb44ae153acfc20c8b8259f55262015d226b662","tid":1960244,"uid":162602,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T04:42:54.000Z","msg":"台灣人真係好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f80f9db6152b365e83cb9aadc64042ef985ccc50","tid":1960244,"uid":34189,"like":46,"dislike":2,"score":44,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T04:43:38.000Z","msg":"戳胸就咁算數?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ab204658ae7d97ce3c2a965de57262fa886d9ac","tid":1960244,"uid":5178,"like":2,"dislike":24,"score":-22,"quote":{"pid":"f80f9db6152b365e83cb9aadc64042ef985ccc50","tid":1960244,"uid":34189,"like":46,"dislike":2,"score":44,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T04:43:38.000Z","msg":"戳胸就咁算數?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T04:45:40.000Z","msg":"女車長可能70碎呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac9ede66ddeef67e9a8a600799d149e5897e6112","tid":1960244,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T04:50:28.000Z","msg":"sauce:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=720445\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D720445&d=IFfiXVp8wSeEFxWCfbiPLS9NcCfN%2BV0%2B2kMkFhSspzA%3D&h=a372a007\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D720445&h=d4065eb8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=720445</a>"},{"pid":"5e42662d06b1c6032464c9152cd144f79d293eb1","tid":1960244,"uid":209657,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T04:57:41.000Z","msg":"據台鐵局統計，昨天未戴口罩經處理，包含自行購買或車站提供之後進站乘車的乘客有520位，未戴口罩經勸離後未搭乘的旅客有186位。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"546c1cb934a2380cd46b04ba6777a1e8e3d25d03","tid":1960244,"uid":209657,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T04:58:25.000Z","msg":"據了解，該名女列車長事後非常難過，也造成基層恐慌。這是台鐵4月1日實施全面戴口罩以來，乘客屢勸不聽，以致於列車延誤最久的一次。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n台鐵局表示，昨已對當事人進行慰問，並肯定其表現。台鐵局說，遇到類似狀況都有訂定相關SOP（標準作業程序），列車長角色是勸導，勸導無效會請路警協助，路警有公權力可以蒐證並開罰。"},{"pid":"c524a127cffd0721236bae8655ed5358c233e4ea","tid":1960244,"uid":262095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T05:02:50.000Z","msg":"趕入大陸"},{"pid":"680d73cf8cc344cff7692eeae85f9697f463b879","tid":1960244,"uid":87339,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T05:04:08.000Z","msg":"睇標題估計係新北<br />\n<br />\n睇内文確認係新北<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60a09ba127aa11dceacd8cbefc19747706298104","tid":1960244,"uid":56731,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T05:05:15.000Z","msg":"佢想攞個胸圍當口罩啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa884624bbb4a5b51270c4cc78c17640405a2041","tid":1960244,"uid":126100,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"680d73cf8cc344cff7692eeae85f9697f463b879","tid":1960244,"uid":87339,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T05:04:08.000Z","msg":"睇標題估計係新北<br />\n<br />\n睇内文確認係新北<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime"